▄I'm loving memory of James Robert Murphy
22nd February 1995 - 25th September 2015
First class philosophy student, football player and founder of the Philosophy team,
treasured brother, son and friend, who gave his life to save another.
"Love: it will not betray, dismay, or enslave you. It will set you free, to be the man you were made to be.""¾
